{
  "feature": "Intelligent Task Prioritization",
  "description": "# Intelligent Task Prioritization\n\nUse ML to analyze task patterns and suggest optimal task ordering based on dependencies, estimated complexity, and historical completion data. Help users focus on high-impact tasks first.\n\n## Rationale\nEnhances the planning phase by providing data-driven task prioritization. Addresses the complexity of managing multi-task workflows. Creates a smarter orchestration layer that learns from usage patterns.\n\n## User Stories\n- As a developer with a complex backlog of tasks, I want intelligent suggestions on which tasks to tackle first so that I can maximize productivity\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] System suggests optimal task ordering based on dependencies and complexity\n- [ ] Priority suggestions improve based on historical completion data\n- [ ] Users can accept, reject, or modify suggested priorities\n- [ ] Explanation provided for why certain tasks are prioritized\n",
  "created_at": "2026-03-16T00:03:08.299Z",
  "updated_at": "2026-03-18T16:25:47.917Z",
  "status": "in_progress",
  "workflow_type": "feature",
